reviewText: P.E. is still the "real deal" and this 5 disc set shows everyone why! They have come a long way and I respect the fact that they never sold-out or conformed as some would say, to be hot or popular for commercial success purposes!

This set is the BOMB! Thank you Public Enemy for over 20 years of politically charged music that makes you think and is LOUDER than a BOMB! The Hip Hop Gods DVD was the best experience I had travelling and performing with classic Hip Hop Gods and Goddesses! Love them all for creating a memorable bond while travelling the countryside! PEace, 1/2pint- Son of Bazerk/No Self Control
